We are using 2 Kraken x60’s to deploy 2 climbers. We really just want 2 positions, up and down. The 2 climbers are independent.

Should we work off of any of the Phoenix 6 Java Examples? Also does the Kraken x60 show up as a TalonFX?

Thanks

Clayton_E:

Also does the Kraken x60 show up as a TalonFX?

Kraken is the motor, TalonFX is the motor controller. Both are necessary to make it work, but the Kraken (and Falcon500) happen to have them ibtegrated into a single unit.

But yes, in code you would control a TalonFX object.
